        <mxCell id="BOTzpaHG5GplE9pYi8ou-78" value="&lt;h1&gt;Distributed Fees System&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;To improve efficiency and reduce costs, DEMOS network is able to manage a variety of distributed gas tanks. This way, paying for gas become a natural extension of how DEMOS works, with a single metacontext encompassing everything from TXs to gas.&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
